data.title: Partnership
data.text:
There is absolutely zero cost to you to bring Yashu Washu to your residential/office building. We take care of all costs of install and operation.

Our 24/7 lockers don't need any utilities, it's zero running cost for you.

Different customers have different needs! that's why we have both FREE pick up & delivery and 24/7 lockers. When one works great with customers that have a hectic schedule other works with these with disabilities.

Communication with us is lightning speed. We get back to you right away. We will meet you, advise you on service location and get to know each other.

Our contract is simple, short and definitely to the point. The best part is you can cancel our service at anytime, no one likes to be restrained anymore. You are in charge.

Yes, not only it won't cost you a dime, but we will give you dimes back! We do a profit share on a monthly basis with our partner buildings. We will talk about that when you call us :)

Most importantly you will be bringing in a 5 star rated cleaners. We do that because we care about our customers and their clothes. A little genuine care goes a long way+ a pint of love.

Since day one we are the most innovative Eco friendly cleaners and we don't plan on stopping. Your tenants will be constantly welcome with new improved green changes.

Keeping your tenants happy with our service, will have a positive effect on your renewals and overall happiness at the property- and that could mean more money :)
